(gen_random_uuid(), '726a4454-a597-49f4-a4e6-42be6ba3da84', 'üî• PRO TIP: Want your gel polish to last 3+ weeks without chipping? Here''s my secret formula:\n\n1. Dehydrate nails with 70% alcohol (not acetone!)\n2. Ultra-thin base coat - cure 30 seconds\n3. Color in 3 THIN coats, curing between each\n4. Cap the free edge with top coat\n5. Cuticle oil daily (this is KEY!)\n\nBonus: Use a glass file for shaping - it seals the nail edge better than emery boards! Your clients will notice the difference üíÖ #ProTips #GelPolish #NailTech', 'tip', 'nails', ARRAY['gel-polish', 'pro-tips', 'nail-tech'], ARRAY[], 156, 42, true, NOW() - INTERVAL '6 days'),

(gen_random_uuid(), '726a4454-a597-49f4-a4e6-42be6ba3da84', 'Makeup artists - stop using setting spray wrong! ‚ùå Most people spray their face directly. ‚úÖ Spray your beauty sponge/brush instead, THEN blend. This technique:\n\n‚Ä¢ Prevents makeup from moving\n‚Ä¢ Creates airbrushed finish\n‚Ä¢ Makes foundation last 12+ hours\n‚Ä¢ No more cakey look\n\nTried this on 50+ clients - 100% success rate! Game changer for oily skin especially üôå #MakeupTips #SettingSpray #ProMUA', 'tip', 'makeup', ARRAY['makeup-tips', 'setting-spray', 'pro-techniques'], ARRAY[], 203, 67, true, NOW() - INTERVAL '7 days'),

