(gen_random_uuid(), '726a4454-a597-49f4-a4e6-42be6ba3da84', 'B√≠ quy·∫øt t·∫°o ki·ªÉu t√≥c cong t·ª± nhi√™n m√† kh√¥ng c·∫ßn m√°y u·ªën! üíÅ‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è\n\nüå∏ T√≥c ∆∞·ªõt: Braid loosely (t·∫øt l·ªèng) tr∆∞·ªõc khi ng·ªß\nüå∏ S√°ng mai: G·ª° b·ªè, x·ªãt sea salt spray\nüå∏ Vu·ªët nh·∫π b·∫±ng tay (kh√¥ng ch·∫£i!)\nüå∏ Finish v·ªõi hair oil ·ªü ƒëu√¥i t√≥c\n\nK·∫øt qu·∫£: S√≥ng t·ª± nhi√™n nh∆∞ n√†ng ti√™n c√°! Ph√π h·ª£p m·ªçi ƒë·ªô d√†i t√≥c. M√¨nh l√†m th·∫ø n√†y 3 nƒÉm r·ªìi, t√≥c kh·ªèe m√† ƒë·∫πp ‚ú® #HairTipsVN #NaturalWaves #VietnameseHair', 'tip', 'hair', ARRAY['hair-styling', 'natural-waves', 'vietnamese-tips'], ARRAY[], 98, 29, false, NOW() - INTERVAL '9 days'),

(gen_random_uuid(), '726a4454-a597-49f4-a4e6-42be6ba3da84', 'SKINCARE GAME CHANGER: The 7-skin method that cleared my hormonal acne üåü\n\nForget expensive serums - this Korean technique using ONE toner:\n‚Ä¢ Apply toner with palms\n‚Ä¢ Pat gently until absorbed\n‚Ä¢ Repeat 7 times\n‚Ä¢ Follow with moisturizer\n\nAfter 30 days my skin texture completely transformed. Key is using alcohol-free, hydrating toner. Takes 5 minutes but worth every second! #KoreanSkincare #SevenSkin #AcneTips', 'tip', 'skincare', ARRAY['korean-skincare', 'seven-skin', 'acne-tips'], ARRAY[], 267, 84, false, NOW() - INTERVAL '10 days');

